{
  "narration": "The ruins of the chapel are bathed in pale, eerie light from the spectral candles flickering silently along the walls. The broken altar looms ahead, dark stains spiraling in ominous patterns across the floor. As you cautiously move forward, the scuffle of tiny claws on stone draws your attention. Suddenly, three giant rats burst from the debris-strewn corners, their beady eyes reflecting a feral hunger as they rush toward you, squealing aggressively. You steel yourself, gripping your weapon. The initiative order is clear: You act first, followed by the second giant rat, then the first, and finally the third. The tension is thick, the cold air holding its breath. Now, Norn, what is your move? Please tell me what action you want to take, and remember to roll your attack dice when ready.",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "narration": "You step forward decisively, longsword in hand, aiming to strike the nearest giant rat. Please roll a d20 for your attack and add your attack modifier of +5 to the roll. Remember, your longsword hits on a 19 or 20 as a critical due to your Improved Critical feature. Let me know your total.",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "narration": "Your attack roll is 15 plus 5, totaling 20. That definitely hits the giant rat's AC of 12! Roll your damage dice for the longsword, which is 1d8 plus your +3 damage bonus. Please roll your d8 and tell me the result.",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "narration": "You bring your longsword down with precision, dealing 10 points of slashing damage to the first giant rat. The creature squeals in pain, blood seeping from the wound but it still stands, snarling fiercely. Now, the second giant rat races forward to attack. It snaps its sharp teeth at you. Using a prerolled d20 of 3, plus its +4 attack bonus, it rolls a total of 7 - far short of your AC 19, and the bite misses!\n\nThe first giant rat tries to bite next. Rolling a prerolled d20 of 19 plus its +4 bonus, it scores a 23 - a solid hit! It bites into your arm. The damage roll is a prerolled d4 of 1, plus 2 damage bonus, totaling 3 piercing damage.\n\nThe third rat lunges at you last, rolling a prerolled d20 of 15 plus 4, totaling 19 - another hit! It also sinks its teeth in. Prerolled d4 damage is 3 plus 2, for 5 piercing damage dealt.",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "C03-E2",
        "changes": "First giant rat takes 10 slashing damage, HP reduced from 7 to -3. Status changed to dead."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateCharacterInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "characterName": "Norn",
        "changes": "Takes 8 points of piercing damage from two giant rats' bites, reducing HP from 31 to 23."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "narration": "You swing your longsword with deadly precision, slicing into the nearest giant rat. With 10 points of slashing damage, you reduce it from 7 to -3 hit points, and the creature collapses dead to the floor. The second giant rat bolts forward, snapping its teeth at you. Using its attack roll of 3 plus 4, it only totals 7, far too low to hit your AC of 19, and misses entirely. The third giant rat lunges next, rolling a 15 plus 4 for a total of 19, which hits! It bites into you, dealing 5 piercing damage. You grit your teeth, feeling the sting as your HP drops from 23 to 18. The battle continues with two rats left standing. What will you do next?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "C03-E2",
        "changes": "First giant rat takes 10 slashing damage, HP reduced from 7 to -3. Status changed to dead."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateCharacterInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "characterName": "Norn",
        "changes": "Takes 5 points of piercing damage from the third giant rat's bite, HP reduced from 23 to 18."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "narration": "You lash out at the second giant rat with your longsword, rolling an 18 plus your +5 attack bonus for a total of 23 to hit, which is a solid hit against the rat's AC of 12! With your damage roll of 5 plus 3, you deal 8 points of slashing damage. The second giant rat shrieks in pain, its health dropping from 7 to -1 as it collapses, dead before it can retaliate. Now, the last remaining giant rat snarls and lunges at you. With a prerolled d20 of 15 plus its +4 attack bonus for a total of 19, it hits! The damage roll is a prerolled d4 of 1 plus 2 damage bonus, dealing 3 piercing damage to you. Your HP falls from 18 to 15. The fight narrows to the final rat. What do you do next?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "C03-E2",
        "changes": "Second giant rat takes 8 slashing damage, HP reduced from 7 to -1. Status changed to dead."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateCharacterInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "characterName": "Norn",
        "changes": "Takes 3 points of piercing damage from the third giant rat's bite, HP reduced from 18 to 15."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "narration": "You swing your longsword at the last giant rat with a fierce determination. Your attack roll of 16 plus 5 totals 21, easily hitting the rat's AC of 12. With your damage roll of 4 plus 3, you deal 7 points of slashing damage. The rat lets out a final squeal as it is struck down, its 7 hit points reduced to 0. All the giant rats have now been defeated. The Ruined Chapel quiets, save for your steady breathing and the ghostly flicker of spectral candles. You stand victorious, though slightly battered. How do you wish to proceed?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "C03-E2",
        "changes": "Third giant rat takes 7 slashing damage, HP reduced from 7 to 0. Status changed to dead."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "narration": "All three giant rats have been defeated, and the chapel falls silent once more. You stand victorious, with no immediate threats remaining in this chamber. The eerie flicker of spectral candles and the shattered stained glass create an unsettling but peaceful atmosphere for now. With the combat behind you, what would you like to do next?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "exit",
      "parameters": {}
    }
  ]
}

Combat Summary: {
  "narration": "You have successfully defeated all three giant rats that ambushed you in the Ruined Chapel. Their bodies lie still among the debris, the immediate threat now quelled. The unsettling silence returns, broken only by your steady breath and the faint flicker of spectral candles. For your victory against these three beasts, you gain 75 experience points. With the chapel temporarily safe, you have the opportunity to explore further or tend to your wounds. What do you choose to do next?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateCharacterInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "characterName": "Norn",
        "changes": "Gains 75 experience points from defeating three giant rats."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "exit",
      "parameters": {}
    }
  ]
}
